parameters: 初期スタート・ルイリセット用
プレイヤーのライト設定

A creepy monster is persistently slamming the
carpet.

\n<Monster>Ahh, I've been so impatient. I've been waiting for
someone to come all this time.

\n<Rui>Is this a different monster from the one
before...?
\n<Monster>Why are you silent? Hurry up and help me.
\n<Monster>Do I have to tell you everything?
\n<Monster>As gently as you would hold a baby bird.

\n<Monster>I've been craving lamb sauté for a while now. Ah,
but first, a rose bath.
\n<Rui>...Do you have such luxurious things here?

\n<Monster>You still haven't apologized. Apologize first, you
stupid trash scum.
\n<Monster>Turn your ass this way, you filthy woman.
\n<Rui>...Just to be clear, why should I?

\n<Monster>I'm going to punish a cheeky, dirty bitch like you
by digging into your filthy holes.
\n<Monster>Fine, I'll make it clear which of us is on top.
\n<Rui>Looks like I have no choice but to do it.
\n<Monster>Father! Mother! There's a murderer in our house!!

\n<Rui>What a terribly selfish monster. Just like the
unpleasant nobles that appear in stories.
\n<Rui>This is a woman's room, isn't it.
\n<Rui>Was that... really a monster, I wonder.
